Since then, our project team has been implementing these trends into their strategic planning, and we’re excited to share some of our experiences with you. While we’d love to share the impact that each and every trend has had on our events in detail, the one that really stuck out for us has got to be technology. We’re seeing more and more events using tech as a tool that not only improves the event creation process but enhances your guests’ experience too. Read all about it in our blog: https://www.wrxgrp.co.za/technology-and-the-events-industry/<img src="http://biz-file.com/c/1812/473736-625x156.jpg" alt="Technology and the events industry" width="625" height="156">